        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516589178581-6cd7833ae3b2?w=800&q=80" alt="Two men close together" />
        <div class="id-overlay"></div>
        <div class="id-text">
          <p class="id-label">Identity 01</p>
          <h2>The Side</h2>
          <p>A Side is a gay or bisexual man who prefers intimacy without anal sex — not as a phase, not from inexperience, but because it simply isn't his thing. Sides find deep connection through oral sex, mutual pleasure, and full-body closeness. It's a complete identity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="id-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529333166437-7750a6dd5a70?w=800&q=80" alt="Two men embracing" />
        <div class="id-overlay"></div>
        <div class="id-text">
          <p class="id-label">Identity 02</p>
          <h2>The Short Stop</h2>
          <p>A Short Stop is a gay or bisexual man who occasionally engages in anal sex but doesn't center it in his identity. It's situational, never definitional. Short Stops often find their deepest belonging in Side-centered spaces.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

